      "content": "Hey, i'm writing a paper on constitutional law. can u help me weigh the pros and cons of religious organizations getting exemptions from govt mandates when those mandates go against their faith? like, is it more important to protect religious freedom or to make sure the state stays secular and everyone follows the same rules?",
